  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AdApiFaultDetail_Exception
    This class was generated by the JAX-WS RI.
    ApiFaultDetail_Exception
    This class was generated by the JAX-WS RI.
    CouldNotGetReportingDownloadStatusException
    This exception is thrown if the ReportingServiceManager failed to get the download operation status after multiple retries.
    CouldNotGetReportingMetadataException  
    CouldNotSubmitReportingDownloadException
    This exception is thrown by the ReportingServiceManager when the SubmitGenerateReport service operation that it called does not return a valid response.
    InvalidColumnException  
    ReportingOperationCouldNotBeCompletedException
    This exception is thrown if an attempt was made to poll for a completed reporting results file and the reporting service returns a failed status.
    ReportingOperationInProgressException
    This exception is thrown if an attempt was made to download a reporting results file that is not yet available.
